# Frontend Conventions

## Component Patterns

- Use functional components with TypeScript
- Use shadcn/ui components customized with the Contruo dark theme (see `docs/design/design-system.md`)
- Use Lucide Icons (16px inline, 20px nav, 24px features)
- Font: Inter for UI, JetBrains Mono for formulas/measurement values

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS only -- no CSS modules or styled-components
- Dark theme as default using CSS custom properties in HSL format
- Purple accent (`#8b5cf6`) for primary actions and active states
- Spacing: 4px base unit, `space-2` (8px) as default gap
- Border radius: small and subtle (`rounded-sm` to `rounded-lg` max)
- Shadows: minimal, only on floating elements (dropdowns, modals)

## Layout

- Three-panel workspace: sheet index (left) | plan viewer (center) | quantities panel (right)
- Vertical split with resizable dividers
- Sidebar: 240px default, collapsible to 48px
- Buttons: 32px default height, 28px compact (toolbar)
- Tables: 32px row height, dense, virtualized for large lists

## State Management

- Supabase Auth for authentication context
- Liveblocks for real-time collaboration state (presence, cursors, live data)
- React context/hooks for local UI state (active tool, selected condition, panel sizes)
